data.description: Welcome to 2121 El Rancho Circle, a beautiful 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in the desirable 55+ community of El Grande Estates. *** THIS FANTASTIC HOME QUALIFIES FOR SPECIAL FINANCING THAT COVERS UP TO $15,000 IN BUYER CLOSING COSTS, INCLUDING INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN, OR SPECIAL 100% FINANCING! *** Step inside this nicely upgraded home and discover a well laid-out floor plan that is perfect for your “golden years” living. The primary bedroom offers an en-suite bathroom, complete with a gorgeous spa-like walk-in shower. The kitchen boasts striking two-tone cabinets in sage green and off-white, gleaming white quartz with gold veining, white appliances, and overlooks the large room addition, built with permits. Step outside the sliding doors to your covered patio--perfect for relaxing with a hammock, or dining "al fresco" with friends and family. Enjoy a comfortable atmosphere with ceiling fans in the main living areas and a central A/C and heat system.  This energy-efficient home features dual pane vinyl windows, and a newer roof.  A 2-car garage with an automatic door opener provides ample parking and extra storage. With very low taxes and an HOA fee of only $50/month, this home is a fantastic value. Conveniently located close to shopping and restaurants, 2121 El Rancho Circle is the perfect place to call home. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own one of the best homes in this great community!
